snippet.title: (NO EAS) Spectrum News Crawl - San Antonio, TX - Texas AMBER Alert
snippet.description:
BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED
CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY
TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY
RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE CORPUS CHRISTI TX
1227 PM CST SUN DEC 13 2020

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS
DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THIS IS A CHILD ABDUCTION ALERT ISSUED BY THE TEXAS AMBER ALERT 
NETWORK

THE SAN ANTONIO POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR LAUREN DURISO,
FEMALE, WHITE/BLACK. 8 MONTHS OLD, APRIL 16 2020, 24 INCHES LONG, 18
POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, BROWN EYES, AND WEARING A PURPLE SWEATER AND 
BLUE JEANS.

POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR WALTER JAMES DURISO, BLACK MALE 24 YEARS OLD,
DOB JANUARY 8 1996, HEIGHT 5 FOOT 6 INCHES, 170 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR
BROWN EYES WEARING PURPLE SWEATER AND LIGHT BLUE JEANS, IN CONNECTION
WITH HER ABDUCTION.

THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A WHITE 2017 TOYOTA COROLLA WITH A TEXAS
LICENSE PLATE NUMBER OF K R S 6 0 2 6. THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD
FROM IN SAN ANTONIO, TX

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR
IMMEDIATE DANGER. 

IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE SAN
ANTONIO PD.

NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS SAN ANTONIO PD AT 210-207-7579.

$$

Intro and Outro Music:
"Local Forecast (Elevator)" by Kevin MacLeod
